INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (280,2,'2014-02-02 06:08:12','0000-00-00 00:00:00','\"As a member of Workshop’s Mastermind group, I’ve enjoyed getting to know other talented freelancers by sharing knowledge, business practices, and what is working (or isn’t working) for us in our businesses.\r\n\r\nSo yesterday when four of us in the Mastermind group got to chat via Google Hangout and share our experiences with each other firsthand, I was stoked. It was such a unique opportunity to sit down and chat with other designers and developers…something that unfortunately doesn’t happen all that often. I think we all get so busy with our work and what we’re producing that we forget to reach out and connect with others in our industry - and that’s perhaps one of the most important things we can do.\r\n\r\nWe started by introducing ourselves and a little bit of how we got to the places we are currently in our businesses. We had a variety of skill levels, all the way from a guy who had been doing front-end development for about a year now to a back-end developer who had been going since 1999. We talked about our ideal clients, what we’re working on now (and how it’s going), and what challenges we’re facing in our businesses and how we can improve our skills and really hone our craft to become better designers and developers. I’m really looking forward to getting to know these guys, to sharing what I’ve been learning as I design and work for clients, and to learning from their expertise…thanks a million to Workshop for not only providing us with quality leads, but for setting up such a unique community like this one!\"\r\n\r\nEnjoy your weekend!','Crawford','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2014-02-02 06:08:12','2014-02-02 06:08:12','',0,'http://letsworkshop.com/blog/?p=280',0,'post','',0,NULL);
